narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I gained a good picture of interesting contemporary mathematics and the skills that are needed to approach interesting open problems.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think the course does a wonderful job of what it is supposed to do. A lot of cool topics are presented, and you engage with a specific topic very intensely to give a presentation on it, thus learning a lot about an interesting contemporary piece of mathematics.
